____________________________________________________________________________</text>
        <ReturnType type="Date"/>
    </JadeMethod>
    <JadeMethod name="jssGetNextMonday" id="e84e2ae1-1ef9-4244-ba20-ef8f649f03c1">
        <source>jssGetNextMonday():Date;
// --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Created:		30 August 2001 by cnwdad1
//
// Purpose:		Returns the date of the next Monday following the date of the
//				receiver.  If the receiver is already a Monday, then the following
//				Monday will be returned.
//
// Parameters:	None
//
// Returns:		The date of the next Monday.
//
// Changed On	Changed By	Reason
// ----------	----------	-------------------------------------------------------
//
// --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
begin
	return self - self.dayOfWeek + 8;
end;</source>
        <text>___________________________________________________________________________

              P R O P R I E T A R Y   N O T I C E

This software, in whole and in every part, is proprietary to Jade Software
Corporation Limited at Christchurch, New Zealand and is not to be
reproduced, used or disclosed except upon prior written permission of Jade
Software Corporation Limited.

  COPYRIGHT © JADE SOFTWARE CORPORATION LIMITED 2002 - ALL RIGHTS RESERVED
____________________________________________________________________________</text>
        <ReturnType type="Date"/>
    </JadeMethod>
    <JadeMethod name="jssGetNextSunday" id="b3e173a7-e472-425d-8c55-41ace6c6c896">
        <source>jssGetNextSunday():Date;
// --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Created:		30 August 2001 by cnwdad1
//
// Purpose:		Returns the date of the next Sunday following the date of the
//				receiver.  If the receiver is already a Sunday, then the following
//				Sunday will be returned.
//
// Parameters:	None
//
// Returns:		The date of the next Monday.
//
// Changed On	Changed By	Reason
// ----------	----------	-------------------------------------------------------
//
// --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
begin
	if self.dayOfWeek = 7 then
		return self + 7;
	else
		return self - self.dayOfWeek + 7;
	endif;
end;</source>
        <text>___________________________________________________________________________

              P R O P R I E T A R Y   N O T I C E

This software, in whole and in every part, is proprietary to Jade Software
Corporation Limited at Christchurch, New Zealand and is not to be
